caption.p: Chemical structures of compounds investigated for sedative effects in the study: benzylacetone (positive control); benzaldehyde ( 1); diethylene glycol monoethyl ether (DEGEE) ( 2); p-vinylanisole ( 3); p-anisaldehyde ( 4); acetanisole ( 5); and anisylacetone ( 6). All seven compounds were found in aroma of K1. Only benzylacetone, compounds 1, 2, and 4 were present in aroma of K2. (Compounds are numbered in order of elution from DB-WAX column.).
